Source: lzo
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Tux Mason <tuxmason@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), libc-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: http://www.oberhumer.com/opensource/lzo/

Package: liblzo2
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: routines for compressing and decompressing data using LZO
 LZO is a portable lossless data compression library written in ANSI C.

Package: liblzo2-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libmpc-dev, liblzo2 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development headers and static libs for lzo
 This package provides static libraries, pkgconfig data and header files
 required for development using LZO.

Package: lzo-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Provides: liblzo2-doc
Recommends: vim
Depends: liblzo2-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for LZO
 This package contains man pages for LZO.
